data.name: CancelDateMessage
data.value:
You are about to cancel the appointment that you had scheduled to make your art.
Before you proceed, you should know the following:
1.- The advance that you have already paid, will be returned to LetsTattoo account, which you can use just to make the creation of a new appointment. 2.- The advance will be discounted in partialities if the value of the new advance is less than the recovered. In case it is the same, it will be discounted in full. In the same way, if it turns out that the new advance is greater than the one recovered, you will have to make the deposit of the remaining value to the new advance. 3. The advance can also be transferred as a gift to any of your friends, bearing in mind that it must be the total value of the advance.
Do you want to continue?
